=====================================================================================
Data Schema
=====================================================================================

families
ID | family_name | head_of_house_hold | phone | address | status | information | current | member

people
ID | name | family_id | phone | email | calling |

teachingPool
                (active, less active, part-member, investigator) 
ID | family_id | status  | Lessons Taught | Last Lesson | Next Lesson | Fellowshipper 


companionships
ID | person1 | person2

events
ID | date | category | family | person_id | comment

user
name | hashed_password | salt | access_level

record_status
familyID | status (old record, recently updated, new, needs fix)

changed_field
family_id | column | old_text | new_text

CVS Format
familyname, phone, addr1, addr2, addr3, addr4, name1, name2, name3, name4

